OK...yeah.great....
Fine. no problem

17
00:02:12.763 --> 00:02:14.253
Harry!

18
00:02:15.198 --> 00:02:19.601
l really am ....sorry

19
00:02:30.048 --> 00:02:31.913
lt's alright.it doesn't matter

20
00:02:34.183 --> 00:02:35.946
What happened to you?

21
00:02:36.385 --> 00:02:38.410
He asked her to go the ball with him

22
00:02:38.588 --> 00:02:41.216
What?
-What did she say?

23
00:02:40.424 --> 00:02:42.051
No.of course

24
00:02:44.260 --> 00:02:47.627
She said yes?
-Don't be silly!

25
00:02:48.097 --> 00:02:50.258
She was walking by....

26
00:02:50.466 --> 00:02:54.596
You know l like the way she walks
Could't help it

27
00:02:55.872 --> 00:03:00.070
Actually.she screamed
lt was a quite frightening

28
