What did you do then ?

29
00:03:03.045 --> 00:03:05.605
What else?l ran

30
00:03:09.951 --> 00:03:11.418
Hi.Harry

31
00:03:17.927 --> 00:03:18.951
Hey!

32
00:03:37.151 --> 00:03:38.378
Bloody Hell

33
00:03:51.260 --> 00:03:55.629
What are those?/-My dress robe

34
