its traditionnal that the three champions
four in this case. are the first to dance.

43
00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:11.420
Oh ! There you are

44
00:05:31.260 --> 00:05:35.287
She looks beautiful!
-Yeah.she does

45
00:06:24.487 --> 00:06:26.931
Is that Hermione Granger ?
with Viktor Krum !

46
00:06:29.131 --> 00:06:29.981
No...

47
00:06:46.365 --> 00:06:49.823
Harry.take my waist
-What?

48
00:06:47.002 --> 00:06:48.196
Your hand on

49
00:07:57.396 --> 00:07:59.118
Are you ready ?!!!

50
00:08:27.401 --> 00:08:29.198
Quite a pumpkin head.isn't he?

51
