Besides.the whole point of the Tournament..

60
00:09:33.198 --> 00:09:36.861
lts international
magical cooperation

61
00:09:36.202 --> 00:09:37.965
To make friends

62
00:09:39.471 --> 00:09:42.702
l think he's gotten more than friends
if you ask me

63
00:09:52.417 --> 00:09:55.020
Are you going to ask me
to dance or not?

64
00:09:55.020 --> 00:09:56.487
Not

65
