He's not suitable for you
He's way too old

68
00:10:11.070 --> 00:10:11.434
What?

69
00:10:12.570 --> 00:10:15.164
ls that what you think?
-That's what l think

70
00:10:17.743 --> 00:10:21.611
Next time.ask me before somebody else does!

71
00:10:22.881 --> 00:10:25.042
l'm not your last resort!

72
00:10:25.218 --> 00:10:27.152
