about the Tournament

85
00:13:03.873 --> 00:13:05.738
Actually.we didn't talk at all

86
00:13:15.718 --> 00:13:18.186
Mostly.he wanted me studying

87
00:13:18.654 --> 00:13:20.554
lt's a bit annoying.actually

88
00:13:25.728 --> 00:13:27.719
What's that supposed to mean?

89
