lt just means he tossed this one
to test you

90
00:13:29.866 --> 00:13:33.461
ln a brutal way that's almost cruel

91
00:13:34.137 --> 00:13:40.565
And....l'm scared for you

92
00:13:45.147 --> 00:13:47.547
Luckily you got off last time

93
00:13:56.817 --> 00:14:05.725
Harry Potter
-Cedric

94
