You know the prefect's bathroom
on the 5th floor?

100
00:14:20.516 --> 00:14:23.542
lt's not a bad place
for a bath

101
00:14:25.588 --> 00:14:31.390
Take your egg and mull things over
in the hot water

102
00:15:06.528 --> 00:15:08.325
l will spend 1 night

103
