l'll try putting it in the water
if l were you

104
00:15:26.382 --> 00:15:29.314
Myrtle!

105
00:15:27.350 --> 00:15:29.653
Hi Harry
Long time no see

106
00:15:46.468 --> 00:15:48.902
Not being a bad boy.are you.Harry?

107
00:15:53.340 --> 00:15:57.208
Myrtle.did you say try to
put it in the water?

108
00:16:02.983 --> 00:16:07.613
That's what he did
The other boy

109
00:16:07.655 --> 00:16:09.885
The handsome one

110
00:16:11.992 --> 00:16:14.358
