134
00:18:24.951 --> 00:18:26.612
Are you sure about this?
-Absolutely

135
00:19:26.786 --> 00:19:28.811
For an hour?/-Most likely

136
00:19:35.728 --> 00:19:38.219
You're telling me this now?
You must be joking!

137
00:19:38.431 --> 00:19:40.422
l just...wanted to help

138
00:19:40.967 --> 00:19:43.231
l bet you're right about
Ron and Hermione

139
00:19:43.669 --> 00:19:45.660
