167
00:30:42.450 --> 00:30:45.681
Hey Harry.l'm happy to see you again

168
00:30:47.088 --> 00:30:47.486
l can come back later.sir

169
00:30:48.623 --> 00:30:52.160
Oh.not necessary.Harry
The minister and l have finished talking

170
00:30:41.160 --> 00:30:42.094
l'll be back in a moment

171
00:30:55.094 --> 00:30:56.618
