172
00:30:57.332 --> 00:31:00.668
Oh Harry.do feel free to indulge
in the snacks in my absence

173
00:31:00.668 --> 00:31:04.104
But l must warn you
they're a little bit sharp

174
00:32:35.563 --> 00:32:36.831
Professor?

175
00:32:37.831 --> 00:32:38.889
Professor!

176
00:32:49.089 --> 00:32:51.112
Igor Karkaroff. you have..

177
00:32:08.862 --> 00:32:12.161
Do you understand these terms?
-l do

178
