Unles the witness possess a
genuine name or consequence..

189
00:34:14.927 --> 00:34:17.293
This session is now concluded

190
00:34:16.563 --> 00:34:21.201
Oh.no no no no no.pray
l have 1 more

191
00:34:22.201 --> 00:34:25.295
Tha name....
-Yes?

192
00:34:24.438 --> 00:34:27.566
l know for certain that this person
took part in the capture..

193
00:34:30.976 --> 00:34:33.788
And tortured Frank Longbottom and his wife!

194
00:34:35.980 --> 00:34:38.083
Name.we need a legit name!

195
00:34:37.083 --> 00:34:39.381
Murphy Crouch

196
00:35:02.581 --> 00:35:04.036
Hello father !

197
00:35:05.245 --> 00:35:06.974
You are no son of mine

198
00:35:58.962 --> 00:36:03.831
Sir.Mr Crouch's son
What exactly happened to him?

199
00:36:02.334 --> 00:36:04.564
He was sent to Azkaban

200
