But he had no choice
The evidence is overwhelming

201
00:36:12.845 --> 00:36:14.039
Why do you ask?

202
00:36:14.480 --> 00:36:18.678
lt's just that l had dreamed about him

203
00:36:21.953 --> 00:36:24.649
lt was in the summer
Before school

204
00:36:26.200 --> 00:36:28.794
ln the dream
l was in a house

205
00:36:29.928 --> 00:36:32.055
And Voldemort was there

206
00:36:31.897 --> 00:36:33.728
He wasn't quite human

207
00:36:33.999 --> 00:36:35.466
Wormtail was there too

208
00:36:36.270 --> 00:36:37.839
Has there been other same dreams?

209
00:36:40.839 --> 00:36:43.967
Yes.they are all the same one

210
00:36:46.000 --> 00:36:49.265
Sir.these dreams that l've seen..

211
00:36:49.182 --> 00:36:52.481
You don't think it actually happened
do you?

212
00:36:56.621 --> 00:36:59.681
l think it's unwise for you to linger
on these dreams.Harry

213
00:37:00.000 --> 00:37:02.230
l think it's best if you simple
forget them

214
00:37:06.665 --> 00:37:08.599
Cast them away

215
