217
00:37:39.498 --> 00:37:42.695
Congratulations.your performance
in Black Lake was inspiring

218
00:37:46.895 --> 00:37:47.939
Yes sir

219
00:37:49.374 --> 00:37:51.069
lngenious

220
00:37:55.116 --> 00:37:57.141
lt's not something found everyday

221
00:38:01.554 --> 00:38:03.454
Nor is this

222
00:38:08.459 --> 00:38:10.120
