223
00:38:12.631 --> 00:38:14.690
Verity syrup

224
00:38:14.134 --> 00:38:17.865
3 drops of this and anybody
will spill his darkest secrets

225
00:38:25.910 --> 00:38:29.080
Should you ever steal from my store again..

226
00:38:29.080 --> 00:38:34.218
My hand might just slip
a little of this pumpkin juice....

227
00:38:34.218 --> 00:38:36.186
l haven't stolen anything!

228
00:38:47.633 --> 00:38:49.897
Believe me.l'm going to find out why!

229
00:39:38.650 --> 00:39:40.140
Silence!

230
00:39:52.730 --> 00:39:54.823
As Mr.Diggory....

231
00:39:57.101 --> 00:39:59.262
And Mr.Potter....

232
00:40:00.772 --> 00:40:02.807
Are in 1st and 2nd positions..

233
00:40:02.807 --> 00:40:04.570
They will be the first to enter the maze

234
00:40:05.742 --> 00:40:07.539
Followed by Mr.Krum...

235
00:40:08.046 --> 00:40:10.173
And Miss Delacour

236
00:40:12.183 --> 00:40:16.017
The 1st person to touch the cup
will be the winner!

237
00:40:20.694 --> 00:40:23.296
At any moment a contestant
wishes to leave the contest..

238
00:40:25.296 --> 00:40:30.097
He or she can send red spots
with his wand

239
00:40:30.234 --> 00:40:32.327
Contestants.gather around

240
00:40:17.046 --> 00:40:19.241
On the sound of the canon....

241
00:44:44.441 --> 00:44:45.530
Fleur ?!

242
00:45:33.736 --> 00:45:35.067
Get down!

243
00:45:49.984 --> 00:45:51.246
No.stop!

244
00:46:29.446 --> 00:46:30.488
Harry !

245
00:46:33.688 --> 00:46:34.538
Harry

246
00:46:36.738 --> 00:46:37.588
Harry

247
00:46:41.788 --> 00:46:42.830
Harry !

248
00:46:44.030 --> 00:46:45.166
Reducto !

249
00:47:02.090 --> 00:47:03.523
Thanks

250
00:47:06.060 --> 00:47:09.962
For a moment.l thought
you are going to let me win

251
00:47:14.435 --> 00:47:15.459
Some game.huh?

252
00:47:21.810 --> 00:47:23.300
Go!

253
00:47:34.423 --> 00:47:35.447
l want you to take it!

254
00:47:35.624 --> 00:47:36.784
You saved me!take it!

255
00:47:38.259 --> 00:47:39.419
Together!

256
00:47:53.741 --> 00:47:56.209
You OK?
-Yeah.and you?

257
00:48:03.118 --> 00:48:04.244
Where are we?

258
00:48:09.658 --> 00:48:11.182
l've been here before

259
00:48:16.030 --> 00:48:17.361
lt's Pockick

260
00:48:20.668 --> 00:48:23.159
l've been here before
ln my dream

261
00:48:25.706 --> 00:48:28.197
Cedric.we have to get back the cup!

262
00:48:28.509 --> 00:48:29.168
Now!

263
00:48:29.410 --> 00:48:31.173
What are you talking about?

264
00:48:37.418 --> 00:48:38.578
Get back the cup!

265
00:48:47.661 --> 00:48:48.787
Who are you?What do you want?

266
00:48:49.987 --> 00:48:51.486
Avada Kedavra !

267
00:49:03.544 --> 00:49:05.171
Quick.now!

268
00:49:19.259 --> 00:49:23.127
Father..unwillingly..given

269
00:49:30.403 --> 00:49:38.367
